description: Network 1 Financial Group, Inc., through its subsidiary, Network 1 Financial Securities, Inc., provides broker-dealer services. The company is a registered broker-dealer with the Securities and Exchange Commission, 40 states, and Puerto Rico. It clears various transactions with and for customers on a fully disclosed basis with its clearing broker, Legent Clearing LLC, a FINRA member firm. It offers its broker-dealer services primarily to individual investors, and small and microcap public companies. Network 1 Financial Group, Inc. was incorporated in 1998 and is based in Red Bank, New Jersey.
